                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "cc394ffcab6d4b0dba644",
                    "stepText": "Let's move to finding the moment of inertia. First, for the seesaw's plank (a uniform rod pivoted about its center), please select the correct formula for its moment of inertia.",
