                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "d9b133e6d1224dc08941b",
                    "stepText": "Great. Next, we use the conservation of angular momentum principle when the skater pulls in their arms. Identify the correct relationship that equates the initial and final angular momentum.",
